<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>New Seller Match</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f3f4f6; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f2937;">
    <div style="padding: 32px 16px;">
      <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0;">
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 22px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 54px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);">
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
              <tr>
                <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2ff 0%, #f0fdf4 100%); padding: 30px 34px;">
                  <p style="margin: 0; color: #6366f1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;">Direct Match Update</p>
                  <h1 style="margin: 10px 0 6px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.35; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">{{advisorName}}, a new seller aligns with your profile</h1>
                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">
                    This seller chose to reach out to advisors directly. Their snapshot is below so you can decide whether to initiate contact.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 26px 32px 24px;">
                  <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6366f1; font-weight: 700;">Seller Snapshot</p>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.7;">
                      <li>Industry focus: {{sellerIndustry}}</li>
                      <li>Primary geography: {{sellerGeography}}</li>
                      <li>Estimated annual revenue: ${{sellerRevenue}}</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>

                  <div style="background-color: #eef2ff; border: 1px solid #c7d2fe; border-radius: 18px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 18px; color: #111827;">Why you received this</h2>
                    <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.7;">
                      <li>Your experience and focus areas matched the seller's criteria.</li>
                      <li>You opted in to direct-list notifications from Advisor Chooser.</li>
                      <li>The seller plans to contact advisors without a platform introduction.</li>
                    </ol>
                  </div>

                  <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #111827;">What to do next</h3>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.7;">
                      <li>Watch for a direct outreach from the seller.</li>
                      <li>Update your notes in the Advisor Dashboard after any interaction.</li>
                      <li>Let us know at support@advisorchooser.com if this opportunity is no longer relevant.</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>

                  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 22px 0 10px;">
                    <a href="{{AdvisordashboardUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 26px; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed); color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">Open Advisor Dashboard</a>
                  </div>

                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">Questions? Email support@advisorchooser.com anytime.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p style="margin: 22px auto 0; max-width: 680px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
        You received this because your Advisor Chooser profile matches a seller's preferences. Manage your notification settings in your dashboard.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
